! uMatrix: Personal ruleset recipe
! Title: Personal rulesets for English websites
!
! Lines starting with character "!" are ignored.
! Character "_" is an alias for "currently selected scope".
! An empty line MUST be used to separate distinct ruleset recipes.


Basic uMatrix rules
	github.com *
		* * * block
		* * css allow
		* * frame block
		* * image allow
		* 1st-party * allow
		* 1st-party frame allow
		* googlevideo.com xhr allow
		* youtube-nocookie.com frame allow
		* youtube-nocookie.com script allow
		* youtube.com cookie block
		* youtube.com frame allow
		* youtube.com script allow
		* youtube.com xhr allow
		4chan.org 4cdn.org * allow
		4chan.org google.com frame allow
		4chan.org google.com script allow
		4chan.org google.com xhr allow
		4chan.org gstatic.com script allow
		4chan.org twitframe.com frame allow
		4chan.org twitter.com frame allow
		4channel.org 4cdn.org * allow
		4channel.org google.com frame allow
		4channel.org google.com script allow
		4channel.org google.com xhr allow
		4channel.org gstatic.com script allow
		4channel.org twitframe.com frame allow
		4channel.org twitter.com frame allow
		invidio.us googlevideo.com media allow
		knowyourmeme.com kym-cdn.com * allow
		reddit.com * * allow
		reddit.com embedly.com frame allow
		reddit.com redditmedia.com frame allow
		tineye.com www.google.com * allow
		tineye.com www.google.com frame allow
		tineye.com www.gstatic.com * allow
		translate.google.com * cookie block
		www.google.com * cookie block
		youtube.com youtube.com cookie allow
		_ 1st-party script
        
Github
	github.com *
		_ 1st-party script
		_ githubapp.com *
		_ githubusercontent.com *
		! Required for raw/diff view of some files (e.g. pictures, pdf, svg)
		_ render.githubusercontent.com script
		_ render.githubusercontent.com frame
		_ raw.githubusercontent.com *
		_ raw.githubusercontent.com xhr
		! Required for uploading pictures in comments
		_ github-production-user-asset-6210df.s3.amazonaws.com xhr
		! Required for uploading other files in comments
		_ github-production-repository-file-5c1aeb.s3.amazonaws.com xhr
        
      
